  {
    "hotel_id": "5485703",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/ibis-styles-bangkok-sukhumvit-4/hotel/bangkok-th.html",
    "name": "ibis Styles Bangkok Sukhumvit 4",
    "detail": "Located within approximately 10 minutes walk from Nana BTS Station (via Sukhumvit 6) this hotel offer a good ambiance to enjoy the area. To access Sukhumvit 6, use EXIT 2 from the BTS Station. One plus point about this hotel is that this is a NON-SMOKING Hotel which make us non-smokers feels very comfortable. The Rooftop bar on the 25th floor is recommended to chill and hang out in the evening. Although drinks menu mostly will be alcoholic beverages with less choice of cocktails and mocktails. Room size is adequate with basic amenities. Unfortunately, you will have to bring your own room sandals and toothbrush & toothpaste. Soap and shampoo is provided in an all-in-one Ibis standard dispenser. You can also buy what you need at nearby convenience stores (7-11 is opp of the hotel). The staffs are very friendly and helpful. Overall, we had a very pleasant stay and hope to stay here again when we visit Bangkok.",
